 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search QE Test Analyst Capgemini 8,253 reviews Milford, CT Capgemini 8,253 reviews Read what people are saying about working here. Job details Job Type Contract Full Job Description Duration :8+Months 
Responsibilities : 
Test planning in accordance with testing scope and coverage. 
Identify and implement the processes to detect defects early, prevent defects slipping from QA to UAT / Production 
Develop and maintain automation scripts based on test cases identified for automation. 
Manual testing includes writing and executing functional, smoke, sanity, regression & UI testing. 
Execute and analyze automated regression suites to ensure quality deliveries. 
Participate in agile ceremonies to include daily scrums, sprint planning and retrospectives. 
Drive the Root Cause Analysis of the production issues & improve the process to prevent them. 
Requirement : 
4+ years experience with Manual Testing 
Experience in analyzing the Unit Test Reports, Static Code Analysis Reports 
Testing and ALM Tools: Azure DevOps (TFS), JIRA, GIT, Maven 
QA Skills: Manual + Automation Testing for POS + Digital eCom testing (Mobile & Web app Testing) 
Tools Exp: Selenium, Appium, Azure DevOps, Jenkin, TestNG, Mevan, AWS, Git 
Automated Test Tools: AWS Lambda, Selenium, TestNG, POSTMAN/SOAPUI, Appium, Winium, JSON " 
